   Pet Bedding
<% end %>

<% content_for :body do %>
You can put used hay, straw and sawdust from vegetarian animals like hamsters, rabbits and guinea pigs in with your home compost. Home composting kits cost £10 and are available from:

• Belles Fleurs Nursery
• Bonny's Country Garden
• Le Quesne's Nurseries
• Longueville Garden Centre
• Ransoms Garden Centre
• St Peter's Garden Centre
• Stanley's at Holme Grown

Or put used bedding into the bin along with your household waste.

